DEVELOPER_NOTES
---------------

Author  : Septina Dian Larasati (septina.larasati@gmail.com)
Folder  : apertium-id-ms/

[29.05.2010]
This folder consists the files needed to do Indonesian - Malay translation, including the morphological analyzers compiled
in Foma. The morphological analyzer can be found in "morphological-analyzer-id-ms" folder, and further information provided
in the README file.

Currently this system is still just a prototype of the whole system, where is still without "POS tagger" and "post generator"
modules.

The system only can translate a dummy sentence in Indonesian (with ambiguities).
ID: "perangkat anda mendukung pengiriman pesan teks yang melebihi batas karakter pesan"

How to run:
echo "perangkat anda mendukung pengiriman pesan teks yang melebihi batas karakter pesan" | perl foma-to-apertium.pl xfst-id.bin | apertium-transfer apertium-id-ms.id-ms.t1x id-ms.t1x.bin id-ms.autobil.bin | perl apertium-to-foma.pl xfst-ms.bin

list of the files:
- apertium-id-ms.id-ms.dix.xml   : bilingual dictionary between indonesian and malay. Simply lemma to lemma,
                                   provided only for the dummy sentence above
- id-ms.autobil.bin              : id-ms bilingual dictionary binary file
- ms-id.autobil.bin              : ms-id bilingual dictionary binary file
- apertium-id-ms.id-ms.t1x       : empty apertium transfer rule file, added only for the translation needed in Apertium
- id-ms.t1x.bin                  : apertium transfer rule binary file
- xfst-id.bin                    : Indonesian morphological analyzer binary file
- xfst-ms.bin                    : Malay morphological analyzer binary file                     
- foma-to-apertium.pl            : PERL script to change the Foma format to feed Apertium
- apertium-to-foma.pl            : PERL script to change the Apertium format to feed Foma


***


[31.05.2010]
Change the form of the tags in Morphotactic rule file, from +Noun to <Noun> (plus '+' sign into inside brackets). Remove the 'Bare*' tags,
and make "perangkat" and "pesan" to have 2 analysis (it was commented in the lexical entry to avoid this).
How to run:
echo "perangkat anda mendukung pengiriman pesan teks yang melebihi batas karakter pesan" | ./foma-proc xfst-id.bin 

